(Item #: M0129-Z3-17)
Norwegian tenor (1889-1968), signed photo postcard, shown as Canio in Pagliacci. Blind stamp on front by photographer Setzer, Vienna. Size is 3.25 x 5.25 inches.
PRICE: $35.00 USD









