                                                    $22.55
                                                                            



Prints in 3-5 business days

During its short run of 96 performances in 1894-5, Boosey issued two different editions of the Vocal Score of this operetta. This new edition of the Vocal Score includes all the material that was cut from the first edition and all the revised material.








